    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes. The interior is nice and clean, and it drives like a dream! I've taken great care of it, so it's ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 29900.0,
