      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and the factory M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanical integrity has been prioritized: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis retains its precision with an updated suspension refresh including Bilstein dampers and poly-bushing upgrades. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved performance machine, the drivetrain remains tight, providing the linear power delivery and telepathic steering response this platform is renowned for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Minimal interior wear. Clean title. Maintenance up to date.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
