    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in great shape, running smoothly and looking sharp. It\u2019s been well-loved and carefully maintained, making it the perfect choice for anyone who wants quality without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
