      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54B32 high-compression inline-six. This unit features a recently serviced VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring the chassis handles the 333hp output without fatigue. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with precision, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. It sits on a refreshed suspension setup with Bilstein dampers, maintaining its signature handling profile. While the finish shows light road wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system components and rod bearings\u2014have been fastidiously maintained. An excellent specimen for the purist seeking peak performance and throttle response.",
